{% timenode 2020-05-15 [2.6.3 -> 2.6.6](https://github.com/volantis-x/hexo-theme-volantis/releases/tag/2.6.6) %}

不需要额外处理。

{% endtimenode %}

{% timenode 2020-04-20 [2.6.2 -> 2.6.3](https://github.com/volantis-x/hexo-theme-volantis/releases/tag/2.6.3) %}

